8 An Act relating to smoking in motor vehicles;
defining terms; prohibiting certain act; providing
9 for penalty; requiring deposit of fee in certain
fund; providing for codification; and providing an
10 effective date.
11
12
13 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
14 SECTION 1. NEW LAW A new section of law to be codified
15 in the Oklahoma Statutes as Section 1248 of Title 21, unless there
16 is created a duplication in numbering, reads as follows:
17 A. As used in this section:
18 1. “Marijuana” shall have the same meaning as provided in
19 Section 2-101 of Title 63 of the Oklahoma Statutes;
20 2. “Motor vehicle” shall have the same meaning as provided in
21 Section 1-134 of Title 47 of the Oklahoma Statutes; and
22 3. “Vapor products” shall have the same meaning as provided in
23 Section 1-229.12 of Title 63 of the Oklahoma Statutes.
24
